data.description:
Welcome to your dream Cape Cod Style retreat in the charming Willowood community! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of classic architecture and modern amenities. Step into the heart of the home, where the kitchen awaits with sleek stainless-steel appliances, providing a stylish and functional space for culinary endeavors. The adjacent living room and dining area create an open, inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining friends and family. The primary suite, conveniently located on the first-floor features dual sinks, a rejuvenating soaking tub, and tasteful finishes, it provides a tranquil escape after a long day. Wood flooring throughout adds warmth and elegance, while neutral carpets in the secondary bedrooms create a cozy ambiance. A distinctive highlight of this residence is the bonus room with a private door, offering versatile space that can be transformed into a home office, playroom, or additional bedroom to suit your lifestyle needs.
This private oasis is the ideal spot for morning coffee or evening gatherings, seamlessly connecting the interior to the beautifully landscaped large, fenced yard.
Safety and peace of mind are paramount, with partial impact windows and partial accordion shutters providing protection against the elements. This home not only exudes charm but also prioritizes functionality and security.
Don't miss the opportunity to make this Cape Cod-inspired gem in Willowood your own. Schedule a showing today and discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and sophistication in a home that truly has it all.

Discover Willowood, where vibrant living meets playfulness. Our community boasts a delightful play area with swings, teeter-totter, and tetherball, creating an inviting outdoor space. Nestled close to shopping, dining, and entertainment, Willowood offers convenience at your doorstep. Benefit from proximity to "A" rated schools, ensuring top-notch education. With easy access to major highways, commuting is a breeze. Welcome to Willowood, a place where amenities and location harmonize, making every day a joy.
